PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Ethereum Transaction Analysis App
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: This app allows you to analyze Ethereum transactions in detail. You can view the flow of ether, tokens, data payloads, and more for any transaction on the Ethereum blockchain.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Simply enter an Ethereum transaction hash and our app will decode the transaction data, trace the movement of ether and tokens, and provide detailed insights.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of analysis is provided?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: The app surfaces the sender, recipient, value transferred, gas used, transaction fee paid, and any data payloads. It also traces token transfers and interactions with smart contracts.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, the Ethereum transaction analysis service is completely free to use. We have no paid tiers or subscriptions required.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our Ethereum transaction analysis app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to analyze Ethereum transactions in-depth. You can track transactions, view details like gas used, decode data, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We connect directly to Ethereum nodes to fetch transaction data. Our app then decodes and visualizes this data for easy analysis.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We currently support Mainnet, Ropsten, Rinkeby, and Goerli testnets. More networks will be added soon.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we do not store any user data. All analysis happens locally in your browser using our decentralized app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: The basic version is free to use. We offer a pro plan with advanced features and higher analysis limits.
